text: The lichen moray (Gymnothorax hubbsi) is a moray eel found in the western Atlantic Ocean, around eastern Florida, the Bahamas, and Cuba.Gymnothorax hubbsi at www.fishbase.org. It was first named by Böhlke and Böhlke in 1977.Common names for Gymnothorax hubbsi at www.fishbase.org. ==References== hubbsi Category:Fish described in 1977
